ight-unset\" id=\"SE-410c7531-80f5-4ae5-9356-56ff62eb7fc8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 상대로 하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-205a9b48-ba6a-4992-8136-45f7bc1b5107\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-59084b0c-bb13-452b-b2a2-ff89a63e1ab4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">영업 방법이 주류였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-81c661f1-063c-4ab8-b788-c04866663733\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65e01018-1fcb-47c2-bbcf-72034f3c99ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f065b252-7013-4eda-a59d-91b7f18486b4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ce286e1-128f-4eba-a448-1b363b1cda73\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 IMF 이후에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-01f2c75f-75c1-4112-b6b0-19afb14be622\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2b74646-cca0-43c9-81a6-29203a1db504\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 시장은 급격하게 변화되게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-24b8af01-d635-4112-8540-48896b61f413\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ebe5a45f-e192-4d7c-9443-34c20b64091f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e80a1947-a83d-4304-8dc7-f087e6651878\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7e144f0c-9b47-41aa-8743-010fb5d7f4a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">표준화된 품목을 기반으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bed29dd5-2fdd-4a41-af9a-ab4d46bf75db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87d42a68-ebf0-45b4-8fec-78c91bd567a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단가를 낮춰 제공되는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-356dafae-14e1-4642-b8af-798541309c55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6892a6a2-b3d0-4b41-b499-d4b4525542ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>합판 인쇄 시장</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86d46632-a8ad-4ea7-bd3f-5b19b5a11a75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의 등장입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e7fff83a-378c-4626-9578-f2c0497a8ab0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c293a6d1-2490-47d6-a0ac-c600506e1433\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-907b3c36-3399-4518-ba19-da8a83cb98e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8b7694e-a126-4ecb-a9cc-036a64bdb877\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합판 인쇄 시장은 명함을 필두로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ee62e678-6801-4759-beb5-eb894f689e63\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be26db53-c2d3-41f2-9fe9-fb1199fc9c44\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스티커, 전단 시장을 잠식했으며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d0443f6-74fe-4b10-890e-6113d4720b42\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ae07055-f7cc-426c-9a43-70d8dcaa7175\" style=\"color:#555555;\">심지어는 독판 인쇄 시장까지를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d4b44c4b-2b5e-47f3-aa86-d1c787a22f8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a5e3b17-b31b-493e-8db6-f638bd225cf4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">점령해 버렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b8abaed3-a5d4-4029-86ca-34b03bc16c15\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3851e75-e93a-47e9-a91c-c234a25db930\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb0c7446-a27e-4acf-8101-68ba69607c79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49e74fd8-b75a-42fb-9841-70ca16f1d010\" style=\"color:#555555;\">점령당한 이유는 많지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8132eedf-2f91-43de-a803-72549dc81771\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99766a80-a9cf-42cc-b27e-6a88684395e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 큰 요인으로는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e524f7fb-c9d3-4fcc-8cb2-e5c982f0106c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6aaa5ee8-77e3-47bb-990b-e1f01f0bfc7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가격입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4ff62702-71cf-4910-bb6c-900b07405153\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2f63952f-ba5c-4a75-95f8-eaea5ab314d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-50164ec7-0778-4600-821f-a41a546dd869\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8ed331e-6ee3-419b-bbf7-e21e164a3cdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러 개의 인쇄물을 모아서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-44c06814-31ef-4b84-8fe7-6cbc06f27cac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9cb8999-d965-4f69-9d40-91750e86c226\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄하기 때문에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-df1e3b22-6dc2-4b9e-a4e8-36a153b672f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-94408f8f-3b7f-4ebd-86c4-680f4d4d9bc2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">출력비나 기본 인쇄비를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-333fc3b1-060b-4b24-ac6f-8d5352881bb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db2afc35-b15a-486d-99a0-4d6f2a45d7e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">절감할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ecffaed8-d90b-4baf-9ffc-0d101bbaaae3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb779292-ca49-4a4b-a632-0de948cf7fee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fadd7c33-fa9e-438b-856d-ae1ace9ec451\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-46af74b9-7bd2-4450-8dbf-af2b6a88d38a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 점 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3a3f6375-b3b9-445e-b5ee-ae66c0aff89a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-199e922d-f462-4bff-9bdd-8ff8e4308255\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합판시장은 2000년대 급격한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c6d6f8da-bfb8-49c5-b2a6-63d3513f1261\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-201e8fc8-fa92-492f-9a66-3cc32aa09e4b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">성장을 이루었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0e5ff9b3-4e71-495b-b203-73e6650f6744\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-564569cd-1a31-47e0-8928-f45a7f0b3389\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f9e6d39a-db14-48fb-b3b2-ec3c1755b267\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00f95a9f-bcac-4c6d-957e-daa0976a6c8a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 합판시장이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-088a85db-e537-4325-a27c-419e508258e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3a343fa-d207-4d8b-86e5-21e049c3cd1a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">큰 시장을 독시하고 있을 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-da26415d-f867-460b-9ebc-8a98fcd5f38d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-43c8bfdd-e903-4475-9b19-86035aa7a98e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또 하나의 변화되는 계기가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3ee9f497-2af1-4893-aac1-df6251db6710\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b23b6c3d-34fc-4f2c-bb61-4bdc22455d13\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 인쇄기의 출현</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44264492-2bf7-4996-9e42-c5a8af1d0c6b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fb4f7e1b-416d-4d3d-a955-a587cf317f7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-72f78070-f33d-4167-b9e3-3876ac49bb89\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f40c2c75-95af-43a9-a485-465c21ac87a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3f3348c-65a8-4d7c-999b-db8627ea5859\" style=\"color:#555555;\">HP 인디고를 필두로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c31e3ad-964a-4017-998f-eec8ea244345\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae4e2f53-fc43-4812-b9aa-ea4c914e9ed7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아이젠, 넥스프레스, 리코 장비들이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e4d36d0d-d6ab-4e47-b67c-36953432f238\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-82d8cabe-f1e0-4c72-874a-7688cc487f12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 다품종 시장에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9a819d4d-90ae-4149-bcee-9935c4ffb299\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39d3c542-6ced-4f67-bad2-8c8fe18f7cc9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘의 트렌드에 맞는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8235e91b-2e84-4525-9c9e-ad88e716d42f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-397b3bb8-e880-4a41-9479-02aeb29d9710\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상품들을 출시하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-236957a3-be12-4aef-8139-315e808fa493\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b2d92c7a-b091-4d0e-a442-3aa2f08d9430\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c2ba03b0-8763-43a0-9c6b-260c001c7f3c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d870bdf2-3cb5-4d40-be22-680e0d93ad72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 디지털 인쇄기 사장의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0e1a3209-a7f4-41f3-9e8a-4ff6e9d5e01c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df2b7271-f251-4cd8-b0ff-941bf25b7fb4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">발달은 소량 생산을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fb144ef2-e856-4d6f-be0a-bf33d890e2fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-91137b53-3f66-4fc3-ad92-29f1297775df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주도했으면 이제는 한 시장을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-13bd65cb-d0d9-4a74-8bc5-809113b4c41b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\