\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-93c7ea25-e222-4323-9f0f-e95e57ff5161\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-425b4056-2baa-4e2d-b1dc-b01f3fa4436e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c334a150-eddf-4f89-abe5-57935273e3da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7c755fd-7ee6-4024-bd4d-ba21f6030631\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 변화 속에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e8ae793e-c64b-4823-8954-f39e1a796153\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dca3b0bb-abd6-4490-85c5-5d26f16db9eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 마케팅 시장도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ab52b57a-81e2-4a87-a330-ee36dff358fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0391a9e-97af-4002-ba2f-f16d71fa4b91\" style=\"color:#555555;\">급변하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f2dadc7c-744d-4926-b651-788b95819b3d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4dd231c3-cbcb-4e8f-a596-773d941a3ff4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9f16b5c6-7939-4f6d-94e4-d311a26e210c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0857c06-a046-4b7a-bfc2-fa2291afef98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">과거에는 장치 사업이라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-da9c1199-d5be-4fba-a8ba-50269d292704\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f04f160a-31ae-41e4-ac51-12d04534f3dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기계만 보유하고 있다면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d8981fb9-029e-428c-a1dd-814ee60e43be\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4bc497d-805d-4dc3-b68c-97651585400b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어느 정도의 매출이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5ff4563c-16f2-4daf-9bda-7f1a4e6b9d9e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-251ca3f6-6a85-4d0f-a8e8-117eca9a2308\" style=\"color:#555555;\">따라왔던 시절이 있었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-adaaef23-e8f2-448a-bfa1-c3382ff0923c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aab5b986-2aae-454a-8fd1-f1fbf3a07b79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-96fba7f0-ebf8-4fc7-9365-ab0322a1835d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eba8f930-6461-4218-88c0-36f7e9bcb530\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 가격경쟁은 날로 치열해지고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f38bdd01-e5dc-4d32-a1d1-26127171ed22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31c8272a-c8ca-4dbb-833b-392e445b5aff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다품종 소량 생산의 시장이 커지면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ee0fea15-6c3d-40fd-894f-6bddc6b4b96e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba6dd89b-3777-4877-bcb9-67573f26c6c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제는 고객이 직접 소량의 인쇄물을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-13b9173b-c94e-481e-a7b5-c218118c482c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-153bc2b6-e690-4db7-8136-1d106576d848\" style=\"color:#555555;\">직접 주문하고 발주하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2ce51366-094f-4590-873e-08e9295ce295\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-00a2099d-6c31-411d-bf0d-dc6a20555b0f\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>B2C마케팅 시대</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-630eb992-c885-4a11-b5ae-94d57314e54b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5a5f97d2-2cb8-4d43-97f3-0f69e40cc7c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8f3f39af-bf98-4cc5-874f-7093c63f29ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bbcca29a-0bf6-4245-a967-55c93b281860\" style=\"color:#555555;\">점점 열리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-24559884-2158-4a32-bf24-71a137d6ad52\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b72e917-e2b9-4b3d-885a-556a56bbfa33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-601dc9a6-462f-4481-b95c-23ee1a6f4aa8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6debbde-4f56-4eeb-8cd2-43576ddcab9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81e9e6f6-643c-48ad-ab16-1515b275ff6b\" style=\"\">인쇄 블로그 마케팅 대행</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-189d3c88-bab6-4ff9-9695-a7b5342ca085\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d4e1f6f-9155-4249-bdf3-a854bbe182e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c00e178-50bb-468e-b43a-c879244a5c9e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니에서는 다음과 같은 조건을 기반으로 인쇄 블로그 마케팅을 대행해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3cd5bfe7-6f30-415d-831e-42f26524f02b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81c71f5e-27cc-4ea0-ae28-003d52972873\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5afcfcca-4917-47b3-b4c1-ee8824fb50b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-22d162c8-dcc0-4a50-9f0c-6e9250539e7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d42f0381-c780-4583-8939-9b6e8d2f32ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4cacf987-1445-4ae1-a1d1-a9ba423c6afa\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>1. 저희와 솔루션 계약이 돼야 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9782329b-c3d3-4d23-be2b-87ad17832f2c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2284ae6a-c901-4c67-848b-7f0080e6e0b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54421ada-7a31-4bc3-96de-276405fbbc8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6def42c7-7a67-439e-90e0-45b5238c5840\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그 계약이 되면 그냥 그 업체에 맞춰 블로그를 작성하는 것은 아닙니다. 그 업체의 가장 잘하는 품목과 장점을 요구분석을 통해 파악하고 이 부분을 중점적으로 작성하게 됩니다. 이런 작업을 하기 위해서는 블로그 요구분석 미팅이 선행돼야 합니다. 그 부분도 시간과 노력이 소요되는 작업입니다. 이런 이유로 저희 솔루션을 계약한 업체에 한하여 사전에 시간을 정해서 블로그 미팅을 병행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-061d3b83-fde0-4b81-97ad-7b7f0b8139e2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-48e81dab-f02e-48af-851e-040bb6afada9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d45b397a-bb70-4e53-bec5-0c93ae772122\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d3cd475-816d-4c79-8ed2-f23d4d1258a4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">즉 다시 말해 솔루션 요구분석 미팅과 병행하여 블로그 미팅을 진행하고 있습니다. 그러므로 솔루션을 계약한 업체에 한하여 합리적인 금액으로 블로그 계약을 진행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3a1fbe4-f8d3-4ac9-a87a-7eae7589948e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223873969606/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72313a6c-1446-4b8c-acf2-d4eb8dcfce18\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ba8212e-4d9c-4993-a182-bfcc303ec8ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2eee93fb-9b95-4b57-9978-2f23c4b90d0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-205b1c37-118f-454b-87db-dce36e80ab2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4153e483-eb34-4537-a2d6-d5e46cd9b063\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbe7a54c-8fdd-4446-ba79-cad75fec0ef4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8a999a94-b7d8-416b-b185-77ef2ceffdfb\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>2. 반드시 블로그를 통해 해야 하는 목표가 있으셔야 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8de8944-b929-482d-97db-ad4e12ae78b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f8b3abb0-49a0-492f-bbf1-ffc14a8d3d0b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0b254324-16f7-4e2d-a9c6-d4f10c9a3854\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f63334f-f75c-4bfb-8e60-354f80a7cd2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그 계약을 하시는 대부분의 고객님은 계약만 하면 매출 전화가 폭주(?) 하시는 걸로 착각을 하십니다. 하지만 냉정히 말해 인쇄 블로그는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cc83fbd4-8c60-46f3-947a-cd5fbcdede83\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>꾸준함이 가장 중요한 부분</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6f203f6-35e0-4320-8c67-1df5573d8944\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 1년은 꾸준히 해야 지수나 기타 부분에서 최고의 성과를 얻을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b365f896-110f-46d2-a77b-77c9ebac01e3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c642df66-f2ba-4093-aa3a-71fa5f821171\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8d094f5-a78a-4d8d-9cc8-05e63bdd17f1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00a4b247-57ce-4289-8103-7b95518c1cf5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이를 위해 계약 고객님은 반드시 블로그로 하시고 싶으신 목표 설정이 필요합니다. 일 컨택 회수, 월 매출, 주별 블로그 작성 글 수, 담당 CS 배정, 역할에 따른 배치 등등입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e0f5254a-6c9d-48c1-b4b9-ae156b3c5bbc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4e01547f-57f0-4cb1-b601-f9c48941311c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f24c286-408d-44db-8e94-bf721b0999e2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9cde32d8-9a91-4686-b385-7af47e0ea5fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">계약을 하시게 되면 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 이런 부분에 대한 아낌없는 조언을 함께 진행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e45e6d7a-dfb8-405b-9575-3360671f4d5e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223873969606/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b1cbf72-d618-4080-98b8-158b3d399848\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7b50cded-099b-4670-9266-27b24eb74d20\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-91b76142-1b0b-433a-b18f-36c711680aa6\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>2. 3가지만 결정하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28b45dc9-7897-4269-8ef7-69ec4e9446f7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ff0500be-be68-4a55-9504-4185d8e2c620\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c9a264ed-8ff1-4201-a9b3-fcfd726cb904\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99ab7384-961e-4f4a-8efc-f78fd9666c9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그 계약은 다음 3가지만 결정하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19c1b43f-e357-496b-990a-4c8d83376353\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e97cec7-fa83-46be-a7b5-865fe9ca3ade\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae37f167-c0d8-4f1b-8bed-b9cbc7467c30\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f8fd42bd-86e3-43ac-8d08-8ec67dc0649c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>누가 할 것인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-06bc13e0-7af6-4249-8415-28584b8dab5e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bb374676-71ec-4802-8ad2-7246803bdfe2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>언제까지 할 것인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7d7f42e8-c332-42c0-94b4-9bbb3591a82d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c78b5858-9216-4754-8494-10e2f22ffa28\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>뭘 할 것인가?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8c62e80-7c04-4c94-b90d-2d87315121a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02226222-c23c-48e5-8ad3-2fffeff8cb74\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6fd46f8-7d15-444b-b45e-bec5f8d20b27\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dd77769d-697a-4fdb-972c-18957de3feee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 너무나 당연한 3가지이지만 가장 중요하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71ca3f99-d9e9-4843-a671-fded3fcf1a9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14a19d9a-5f83-4f50-98e5-1eb4f8afd97f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53e0bf23-446a-4182-8670-86eba742e7ea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a73a3a8-68e9-4cea-85c0-357c2c093a6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그 마케팅을 담당한 직원이 있나요?에 대한 질문을 회사 내부에서 치열하게 논의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-867b28c1-869f-4e9d-941f-9657cc7432e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1e8edcd5-1f7d-4f02-bdaf-284987ba485c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2bfeafe6-b641-49fe-a8c6-83d7288ace1a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b5e359aa-eb17-4e42-841a-589dbb347c1c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 이 마케팅을 몇 개월 하다가 중단하면 큰 성과를 이루기 어렵습니다. 지속적으로 언제까지는 최소한 할 건지를 결정해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5698054d-bbe4-4894-9ec8-0adabd66f935\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f290866-0e39-42f1-b689-1113c3196415\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-814ebe05-226a-4b82-b46b-a32f5629124c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e7a2bda-09e7-48b1-9b19-4723d264d52c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 뭘 작성하는 주제를 반드시 정해야 합니다. 여기에는 파는 품목뿐 아니라 회사만의 강점을 노출해야 합니다. 이 치열한 블로그 마케팅 시장에서 살아남으려면 자기만의 장점이 명확히 부각되는 글이 최고의 메리트가 될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f9fcfb4e-0b66-454e-9ba9-4fa0e25f09eb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223873969606/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5560201d-af0a-4bf1-bc09-b431107d4f05\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87baec44-bb0c-4884-b6df-bd61283b63a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-398a4e4d-9970-4623-9afd-e8caf90a17c3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">인쇄 블로그마케팅에 대한 모든 질문은 환영합니다. 계약 유무를 떠나 궁금하신 사항은 언제든지 문의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17331403-f049-4628-9d5c-35959f3beede\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a8284c2-206f-4d39-8bec-a616c25d22a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3810166f-c929-4006-a9a6-f55047729ada\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7254cd7-92bb-48f3-a5d0-c47b96be3a26\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">인쇄회사 전용 블로그도 (주)파파스컴퍼니입니다. 월 비용이나 방법 등 자세한 사항은 상담을 통해 진행됩니다. 블로그에서 가격이나 방법을 공개하지는 못함을 이해하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5fbd307-56b2-4877-b835-0777399f2487\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca0a2a0b-17be-47d4-9f81-5ea09a40c4c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f27759a-eca5-4be7-b4ae-e6ca93b94a41\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2c191325-8c6c-46f0-a36c-37474c956759\" style=\"color:#555555;\">항상 고객의 성장과 함께하고 싶은 (주)파파스컴퍼니입니다. 감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223873969606#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
